# This folder holds the MadGraph C++ to GRANIITTI C++ conversion script
#
# mikael.mieskolainen@cern.ch


A. AUTOMATIC conversion script for MadGraph 'standalone_cpp'

 1. python MG2GRA.py


B. ADDITIONAL MANUAL labour is (currently) required after running the conversion

 1. Check that you have all necessary HELAS routines under HelAmps_sm.cc / h
 2. Check that you have all necessary parameters under Parameters_sm.cc / h
 3. Add the amplitude under MAmplitudes.h
 4. Add the process handle under MSubProc.cc

